-Butt curls 3 set of 15 ⁣
- Weighted Step ups 3 sets of 15 ⁣
-Ball tosses 3 sets 30 seconds ⁣
-weighted Rowers 3 sets 30 seconds ⁣
-Ropes 20 seconds each arm ⁣
